==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bock beer
<hw>Bock" beer`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <ety>[G. <ets>bockbier</ets>;
<ets>bock</ets> a buck + <ets>bier</ets> beer; -- said to be so named
from its tendency to cause the drinker to caper like a goat.]</ety>
<def>A strong beer, originally made in Bavaria.</def> <altsp>[Also
written <asp>buck beer</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bockelet</ent>⟦br⟧
